<H3> <TI>   Zhu Rongji Reportedly To Visit Israel `Before Fall' </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2302143494 Hong Kong WEN WEI PO in Chinese 23 Feb 94 p A2 </F>
<F P=103> HK2302143494 </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong WEN WEI PO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [By staff reporter Wang Sung (3769 2646) in Jerusalem: "Zhu </F>
Rongji Is To Visit Israel Before Fall This Year"] 
  [Text] Jerusalem, 22 Feb (WEN WEI PO) -- (Ayaz) [a ya zi 
7093 0068 5417], director of the Second Asia Department of the 
