<H3> <TI>   Zhou Nan Denies Rumor of Transfer to Beijing </TI></H3>
<F P=102>  HK2402063394 Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO in Chinese 18 Feb 94 p 2 </F>
<F P=103> HK2402063394 </F>
<F P=104>  Hong Kong TA KUNG PAO </F>


<TEXT>
Language: <F P=105> Chinese </F>
Article Type:BFN 

<F P=106> [Report: "Zhou Nan Denies Rumor That He Will Be Transferred </F>
to Beijing"] 
  [Text] Zhou Nan, director of the XINHUA Hong Kong Branch, 
yesterday clarified the rumor that he was to be transferred to 
Beijing. According to Zhou Nan, a rumor of this kind appears 
about once a year and may reappear in the future. He said the 
principle for coping with it was very simple -- "just ignore it." 
  In addition, Deputy Director Zhang Junsheng said that the 
news was untrue and inaccurate. 

</TEXT>

